(1, 'Custom Vape Cartridge Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Vape Cartridge Boxes </span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">One of the best alternatives to smoking is to vape, so in order to showcase\r\nyour vape cartridges, you will need custom vape cartridge boxes. We at\r\ncustomboxesus make sure you get what you are looking for, and for that, we have\r\nthe expertise that can help you in further the process of having custom\r\npackaging. We strive to give you a look that can help you to achieve more\r\ncustomers with our best high-tech printing techniques. At customboxesus, the\r\nmaterial we use is always top-notch, so we pay extra attention to design and\r\nsafety.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Make a statement with customization:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our team at customboxesus takes customization as a serious matter and\r\nstrives to give the best output. We have hundreds of clients that are satisfied\r\nwith our customization. And our customization services include:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Selection\r\n     of raw material.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Styles\r\n     & Font.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The design\r\n     you may want to consider.<o:p></o:p></