argin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Corrugated\r\n     cardboard boxes.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Kraft paper is what we like to use to make Kraft boxes. The Kraft is made of\r\nsolid pinewoods, making it both eco-friendly and durable. Kraft papers are\r\navailable in two colors: brown and white. Custom jewelry gift boxes are what we\r\nmake using both kinds of Kraft boxes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Kraft boxes are available in a variety of sizes and shapes. We also print\r\nCustom Kraft jewelry boxes in a variety of ways.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Cardboard boxes we provide are often in use for jewelry giving. Cardstock is\r\na light substance that can lift up to 1 pound. Essentially, bespoke paper boxes\r\nare more capable of printing in the case of jewelry. On paper boxes, the\r\npersonalized printing looks fantastic.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We can give a variety of personalized boxes made of paper that are well\r\nworth the investment. We also use paper-thin sheets within the bespoke boxes to\r\nprecisely hold the jewelry pieces. Because jewelry is very delicate, we provide\r\na variety of activities to keep it secure.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We provide Custom corrugated boxes to store heavyweight jewels. For example,\r\nyou can use them for thick necklaces, bangles, and so on. These pieces of\r\njewelry are both pricey and practical. So, using bespoke corrugated jewelry\r\nboxes we offer to send it securely is the best option.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Jewelry Boxes of Various Styles</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><o:p></o:p></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);