lor: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our minimum purchase is just 40 wraps. So, you may mix and combine your\r\nwraps to experiment with different wrap designs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Purchase in Bulk<o:p></o:p></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">As much as we would want to provide the lowest costs on the market, we are\r\nunable to match every customer expectation in this area since we design our\r\nwraps only using high-end eco-friendly materials. The main pricing issues are\r\nthe labor resources and the time necessary to hand-construct each wrap.\r\nCustomboxesus is the firm to go to if you want beautifully produced, high-<b>\r\nCustom Flower Wraps</b> that reflect your brand at its best. When you purchase\r\nin bulk, your order may be eligible for a tailored discount.</span></p>', 'custom-flower-wrap-packaging', '1649063033_Custom Flower Wraps.jpg', '1649063033_Custom Flower Wrap packaging.jpg', '1649063033_Custom Printed Flower Wraps.jpg', '1649063033_Custom Wholesale Flower Wraps.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Specifically designed for the export market, our Custom Flower Wrap packaging is water-resistant, strong, and heat-insulated available at Customboxesus.', 'Custom Flower Wrap', 'Custom Flower Wrap packaging', 'Custom Printed Flower Wraps', 'Custom Wholesale Flower Wraps', NULL, 0, 3, 1, NULL, '2022-04-04 13:03:53', '2022-04-04 13:03:53'),
